{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779187472927,"sessionID":"ses_1c02c80f1ffeMPOpX92Fqk2guI","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_00_7ZFe07uuTf4kvLyIYaNO8038","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore backend structure","prompt":"Explore the backend directory structure thoroughly. I need to understand:\n\n1. What files exist under backend/src/modules/ (especially any auth module files)\n2. What files exist under backend/src/core/base/\n3. What files exist under backend/src/core/decorators/\n4. What files exist under backend/src/core/guards/\n5. What files exist under backend/src/core/interceptors/\n6. What files exist under backend/src/core/filters/\n7. What files exist under backend/src/infrastructure/token/\n8. What files exist under backend/src/config/\n9. What files exist under backend/src/shared/\n10. What files exist under backend/test/\n11. What enums exist in backend/src/\n12. What entities exist in backend/src/modules/ or backend/src/database/\n\nFor each directory, list the files (not their full content). Also check if .claude-project/nestfind/status/MISSING_ENDPOINTS.yaml exists and list its content if it does.\n\nReturn a comprehensive listing of the file tree.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_1c02bf81bffeWj0LG6kCjN2bzd (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nNow I have all the information needed. Here is the comprehensive report.\n\n---\n\n## Backend Directory Structure — Comprehensive Listing\n\n### Top-Level `backend/src/`\n\n```\nbackend/src/\n├── main.ts\n├── app.module.ts\n├── common/\n├── config/\n├── core/\n├── database/\n├── infrastructure/\n├── modules/\n└── shared/\n```\n\n---\n\n### 1. `backend/src/modules/` (Feature Modules)\n\n**IMPORTANT**: Currently only **entities** exist in all modules. There are **no controllers, services, DTOs, repositories, or module definition files** yet.\n\n#### `modules/auth/`\n```\nbackend/src/modules/auth/entities/\n├── password-reset-token.entity.ts\n└── refresh-token.entity.ts\n```\n\n#### `modules/users/`\n```\nbackend/src/modules/users/entities/\n└── user.entity.ts\n```\n\n#### `modules/properties/`\n```\nbackend/src/modules/properties/entities/\n├── amenity.entity.ts\n├── property-amenity.entity.ts\n├── property-photo.entity.ts\n└── property.entity.ts\n```\n\n#### `modules/favorites/`\n```\nbackend/src/modules/favorites/entities/\n└── favorite.entity.ts\n```\n\n#### `modules/inquiries/`\n```\nbackend/src/modules/inquiries/entities/\n└── inquiry.entity.ts\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. `backend/src/core/base/`\n\n```\nbackend/src/core/base/\n├── index.ts\n├── base.entity.ts\n├── base.repository.ts\n├── base.service.ts\n└── base.controller.ts\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. `backend/src/core/decorators/`\n\n```\nbackend/src/core/decorators/\n├── index.ts\n├── api-response-data.decorator.ts\n├── api-swagger.decorator.ts\n├── current-user.decorator.ts\n├── public.decorator.ts\n└── roles.decorator.ts\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. `backend/src/core/guards/`\n\n```\nbackend/src/core/guards/\n├── index.ts\n├── jwt-auth.guard.ts\n├── jwt.strategy.ts\n└── roles.guard.ts\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. `backend/src/core/interceptors/`\n\n```\nbackend/src/core/interceptors/\n├── index.ts\n├── logging.interceptor.ts\n├── remove-token.interceptor.ts\n├── set-token.interceptor.ts\n└── transform.interceptor.ts\n```\n\n---\n\n### 6. `backend/src/core/filters/`\n\n```\nbackend/src/core/filters/\n├── index.ts\n├── all-exceptions.filter.ts\n└── http-exception.filter.ts\n```\n\n#### Also under `core/`:\n```\nbackend/src/core/pipes/\n├── index.ts\n└── validation.pipe.ts\n```\n\n---\n\n### 7. `backend/src/infrastructure/token/`\n\n```\nbackend/src/infrastructure/token/\n├── token.module.ts\n└── token.service.ts\n```\n\n#### Other infrastructure placeholders (empty, only `.gitkeep`):\n```\nbackend/src/infrastructure/logging/.gitkeep\nbackend/src/infrastructure/mail/.gitkeep\nbackend/src/infrastructure/s3/.gitkeep\n```\n\n---\n\n### 8. `backend/src/config/`\n\n```\nbackend/src/config/\n├── env-config.service.ts\n└── jwt.config.ts\n```\n\n---\n\n### 9. `backend/src/shared/`\n\n```\nbackend/src/shared/\n├── dtos/\n│   ├── index.ts\n│   ├── pagination.dto.ts\n│   └── response-payload.dto.ts\n└── interfaces/\n    ├── index.ts\n    └── jwt-payload.interface.ts\n```\n\n---\n\n### 10. `backend/test/`\n\n```\nbackend/test/\n├── e2e/\n│   ├── admin-dashboard.e2e-spec.ts\n│   ├── admin-users.e2e-spec.ts\n│   ├── amenities.e2e-spec.ts\n│   ├── auth.e2e-spec.ts\n│   ├── favorites.e2e-spec.ts\n│   ├── inquiries.e2e-spec.ts\n│   ├── profile.e2e-spec.ts\n│   └── properties.e2e-spec.ts\n├── fixtures/\n│   ├── auth.fixture.ts\n│   ├── property.fixture.ts\n│   └── user.fixture.ts\n└── setup/\n    ├── test-app.factory.ts\n    └── test-database.ts\n```\n\n---\n\n### 11. Enums (`backend/src/common/enums/`)\n\n```\nbackend/src/common/enums/\n├── index.ts\n├── inquiry-status.enum.ts\n├── property-type.enum.ts\n├── role.enum.ts\n└── user-status.enum.ts\n```\n\n---\n\n### 12. Entities (All)\n\n```\nbackend/src/core/base/base.entity.ts\nbackend/src/modules/auth/entities/password-reset-token.entity.ts\nbackend/src/modules/auth/entities/refresh-token.entity.ts\nbackend/src/modules/favorites/entities/favorite.entity.ts\nbackend/src/modules/inquiries/entities/inquiry.entity.ts\nbackend/src/modules/properties/entities/amenity.entity.ts\nbackend/src/modules/properties/entities/property-amenity.entity.ts\nbackend/src/modules/properties/entities/property-photo.entity.ts\nbackend/src/modules/properties/entities/property.entity.ts\nbackend/src/modules/users/entities/user.entity.ts\n```\n\n---\n\n### 13. `backend/src/database/`\n\n```\nbackend/src/database/\n├── migrations/\n│   └── 001-initial-schema.ts\n└── seeders/\n    └── .gitkeep\n```\n\n---\n\n### 14. MISSING_ENDPOINTS.yaml\n\n**Does NOT exist.** Searched at:\n- `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/MISSING_ENDPOINTS.yaml`\n- `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/status/nestfind/MISSING*` (any variant)\n\nThe only status files present under `.claude-project/` are:\n\n| File | Location |\n|------|----------|\n| `seed.yaml` | `.claude-project/nestfind/status/seed.yaml` |\n| `PIPELINE_STATUS.md` | `.claude-project/nestfind/status/PIPELINE_STATUS.md` |\n| `INIT_REPORT.md` | `.claude-project/nestfind/status/INIT_REPORT.md` |\n| `DESIGN_STATUS.md` | `.claude-project/nestfind/status/DESIGN_STATUS.md` |\n| `DESIGN_FULL_GENERATION_REPORT.md` | `.claude-project/nestfind/status/DESIGN_FULL_GENERATION_REPORT.md` |\n| `DATABASE_SCHEMA_REPORT.md` | `.claude-project/nestfind/status/DATABASE_SCHEMA_REPORT.md` |\n| `BACKEND_TESTS_GENERATED.md` | `.claude-project/nestfind/status/BACKEND_TESTS_GENERATED.md` |\n| `PIPELINE_STATUS.md` | `.claude-project/status/nestfind/PIPELINE_STATUS.md` |\n| Various `.blueprint-*.json` files | `.claude-project/nestfind/status/` |\n| Various `.gate-proofs/*.proof` files | `.claude-project/nestfind/status/.gate-proofs/` |\n\n---\n\n### Key Observation\n\nThe backend has a well-structured **core layer** (base classes, guards, decorators, interceptors, filters, pipes) and the **entity layer** is populated across all five feature modules (auth, users, properties, favorites, inquiries). However, the **module, controller, service, repository, and DTO layers are entirely missing** for all modules. The infrastructure layer has only the `token` service/module implemented; `mail`, `s3`, and `logging` are empty placeholders. The `shared/` directory is populated with shared DTOs and interfaces.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_1c02c80f1ffeMPOpX92Fqk2guI","sessionId":"ses_1c02bf81bffeWj0LG6kCjN2bzd","model":{"modelID":"deepseek-v4-pro","providerID":"opencode-go"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore backend structure","time":{"start":1779187320807,"end":1779187472926}},"id":"prt_e3fd3e5dc001cXK92RX2DRC4K3","sessionID":"ses_1c02c80f1ffeMPOpX92Fqk2guI","messageID":"msg